description: Mamu Thai Noodle is roaming the streets of New York. Our mission is to bring the Thai experience to YOU on the streets of New York City with our authentic Thai noodle dishes! From perfect Pad Thai to mouthwatering boat noodles, our menu of delights has something to satisfy everyone from noodle novices to seasoned enthusiasts. We use family recipes that have stood the test of time for generations. Mamu Thai Noodle is family owned and operated.
name: Mamu Thai Noodle
